Package: homologiser
Type: Package
Title: Map Genes To Their Homologues In A Different Species
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Russ Hyde, University of Glasgow
Maintainer: Russ Hyde <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Provides some helper functions that make it easy to map from a
  set of genes to their homologues in another species. One-to-one homologues
  can be returned if requested. Uses Ensembl (biomaRt) databases.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/russHyde/homologiser
BugReports: https://github.com/russHyde/homologiser/issues
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
Imports: dplyr,
    magrittr,
    RCurl,
    biomaRt
Collate:
